data.description: Fall in love with this fantastic 4 bedroom 3 full bath home plus bonus room with lots of upgrades! Welcoming rocking chair front porch with tongue/groove ceiling that leads guests to the spacious foyer with wainscoting! Owners suite on 1st floor! Low maintenance LVP flooring, 8 ft doors & custom shades! Living room with vaulted ceiling, gas fireplace, ceiling fan & sliding doors to fantastic screened porch with tongue/groove ceiling! Gourmet kitchen with quartz countertops, huge island with breakfast bar, farmhouse sink, pantry, 6 burner gas stove with 36 inch oven, custom venthood, built in microwave & dishwasher! Dining room! Office with coffered ceiling, custom built ins & french doors! Owners suite with tray ceiling, fan, sitting area, bathroom with walk in tiled shower, walk in closet & double sink quartz vanity! Spacious spare bedrooms! Beautiful full hall bathroom with double sink vanity, framed mirrors, tiled shower & flooring! Upstairs bedroom with walk in closet & full bathroom with tiled shower! Laundry room with utility sink! Nice fenced backyard with added patio! Side entry 2 car garage with man door! Great location with easy access to SRS, Fort Eisenhower & much more!
